<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">u have to create a new shelf and rename it to your liking such as &apos;To-avoid&apos; and mark the books to this name. sadly, thr s no to-avoid or ignore kinda<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">u have to create a new shelf and rename it to your liking such as 'To-avoid' and mark the books to this name. sadly, thr s no to-avoid or ignore kinda shelf provided by good reads. you have to create one<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
